#id=1
#text=Baking a cake and be fun and eating the cake even more fun .
#id=2
#text=I have made cakes homemade from scratch using a recipe from my mom .
#id=3
#text=But most of the cakes I have made have been from a box mix .
#id=4
#text=I recently made myself a birthday cake .
#id=5
#text=I made a German chocolate cake and it was delicious .
#id=6
#text=Most box mixed call for a couple eggs and water .
#id=7
#text=Sometimes you have to add oil also .
#id=8
#text=The German chocolate cake I made called for oil and I used coconut oil .
#id=9
#text=When you bake a cake you always have to oil and flour the cake pan so it does not stick .
#text=I used two round cake pans for my birthday cake but I have often used a square pan or a bunt pan .
#text=After taking a cake out of the oven you need to let it cool .
#text=I was eager for my birthday cake to cool so I could frost it .
#text=German chocolate cake typically has a coconut and pecan frosting and this is what I used .
